page.title: 20Housing /Jacob Cowens
page.content: These topics begin on another page. {Houses. terraced in J3 and one in J4.In J3 six people live in a semi-detached houses and eleven in J4.In J3 fourteen people live in detached houses and also fourteen in J4.In J3 one person lives in a cottage and two people in J4.In J3 twenty people live in a house and nineteen people in J4.In J3 four people live in bungalows and five in J4.One person lives in a flat in J3 and also the same in J4.Then we asked them whether they rented or owned their houses.Four people in J3 and two in J4 rent their houses.In J3 twenty people own their houses and twenty six in J4. {Jacob Cowans at Dalston. drainage pipes. Mr Coulthard said of the future,"Times are hard but touch wood we will keep going."
